# Requested New Features and Suggestions

This file is dedicated to those who are interested in this project and need some extra features or some modifications.
You need to add the Feature and a short description about the feature in a new passage/section seperated by a new line.
The highest priority will be given to the feature, which requested first, and so on.
This is a example feature request.

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
name - face recognition
description - identification of human faces in a selected image. 
mail ID/GitHub ID - name@mail.com
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
